	quest.030E9B31D4831406.quest_desc: [
		"Voltage and Current gauges are great as they allow the player to measure the associated values in an electrical network."
		"Voltage is the electrostatic potential between two points, so it's terminals can be connected between any point and no electricity will flow between them."
		"Current is the flow of electrons, measured in Amps, Therefore, in order to measure, it must be connected in series with whatever point is connected."
		""
		"&oPonder for more details&r"
		""
		"{@pagebreak}"
		""
		"Picking these up and placing them wherever you need to measure can obviously be very frustrating. You should try to obtain a multimeter! It's a handheld version of both, however, the recipe is expensive with electrical components! I'm not giving that out for free!"
	]
	quest.030E9B31D4831406.quest_subtitle: "Obtain a Voltage and Current gauge"
	quest.030E9B31D4831406.title: "Gauge the Situation"
