	quest.1F7B419E6EF4C80D.quest_desc: [
		"The grappling wisk tethers the player to stationary or valkyerian skies blocks!"
		"While it is named as a form of grappling hook, it will only tug gently to help players maneuver."
		"This can be helpful in situations where:"
		"- your hot airballoon is leaving without you!"
		"- getting sucked up in a tractor beam against your will"
		"- maneuvering in orbit"
		"- swinging tarzan style tree to tree"
	]
	quest.1F7B419E6EF4C80D.quest_subtitle: "Obtain a grappling whisk"
	quest.1F7B419E6EF4C80D.title: "Spider-time"
	quest.1F9600E15698FCE2.quest_desc: [
		"Propellers can be used to generate propulsion in the air!"
		"Their efficency is based off of three things, the input rpm applied, the amount of blades attatched, and the type of blade."
		""
		"Different blades have different effects in water and air, try them out!"
		""
		"[Tip]: Using a &nshovel&r in water whilst on a physics contraption allows you to row like you would with a boat!"
		""
		"&oPonder for more details&r"
	]
	quest.1F9600E15698FCE2.quest_subtitle: "Obtain and use a propeller"
	quest.1F9600E15698FCE2.title: "Wright brothers fright"
	quest.20858C0A76C83E2F.quest_desc: [
		"Transformers \"Transform\" electricty by swapping out current and voltage in a circuit. They are an amazing way to step up or down the voltage in an electrical network and are nessacary for long distance energy transfer."
		"They will manipulate voltage in the ratio between coils."
		""
		"&oPonder for more details&r"
		""
		"[Note(s)]:"
		"- When right clicking on the body to change coil #, HOLD right click, it take a second for the menu to pop up."
		"-Transformers only work in AC, and this is were the whole AC/DC thing gets wonky, technically the three phase power generated by your induction generator should have already done this, but we don't question it."
	]
	quest.20858C0A76C83E2F.quest_subtitle: "Obtain a Transformer"
