	quest.5E5E00F4F1AA9F4E.quest_desc: [
		"The Create mod is all about machines. One of the biggest puzzles of the mod is &opowering&r said machines!"
		"     Create uses a unqiue power system through rotational kinetics! &oshaft-like or rotation transmitting objects&r transmit rotational energy through shafts and alike machines to allow for the functionality of most!"
		"     Increasing the shaft's &orotational velocity&r [rpm] greatly improves the speed at which create mod machinery functions! This comes at the drawback of increased &o[su] or stress units&r *at a cap of 256 [rpm]*"
		"     [su] or &oStress Units&r is the &ncost&r in this energy system and is somewhat equivalent to torque. All Machinery Requires [su] and it is drained from the total rotational network every time new machinery is added. The amount of [su] a machine uses is multiplied from it's current [rpm]- so be careful not to overstress your network"
		""
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"For example, the handcrank this task requires produces 256 [su] in the network at 8 [rpm]. In otherwords, 32 [su] per [rpm]. Therefore, you could power 1-2 machines from it's energy alone before the network overstresses."
		""
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"Holding [W] on most create mod items will allow the user to engage in a &oponder&r."
		"This shows the player a visable depiction of how to use a item/block without the use of an online wiki. Use this and what you've learned about JEI to complete this task and learn about create!"
	]
	quest.5E5E00F4F1AA9F4E.quest_subtitle: "Obtain a Handcrank and Learn About [su] vs [rpm]"
	quest.5E5E00F4F1AA9F4E.title: "You're Cranking What?"
	quest.5E71DC3E47F06970.quest_desc: [
		"The stock system in create can be quite confusing, so we'll take this one step at a time. The packagers created in the last quest can be mounted with a &nstock link&r. These links can be connected to a stock network by right clicking on any stock(ticker/link) already in a network. Stock links inside the network will connect the inventories of the packagers they're connected to into the network's stock ticker. The ticker allows the player to view the contents of all inventories, and order from them aswell! Ordered packages will come out of the packagers they are attatched to, therefore- the player must build their own logistics system to conglomerate these \"inventories\""
		""
		"{image:createdieselgenerators:item/lighter_ignited width:25 height:25 align:center}"
		""
		"&oYOU SHOULD PONDER FOR MORE DETAILS&r"
	]
	quest.5E71DC3E47F06970.quest_subtitle: "Obtain an use a stock link/ticker network to expand your personal inventory"
	quest.5E71DC3E47F06970.title: "Extended Inventory"
	quest.5EBB04151AD1E8D4.quest_desc: [
		"Gearboxes and chaindrives are very similar items, however:"
