		"-Gearboxes have multiple openings with inversed rotation on each side, &lright click a gearbox to rotate it vertically&r and have shaft outputs on it's top"
		""
		"-Chaindrives are different in that they act like small cogs in series- yet rotation does not flip across blocks &nand&r rotatoin can be flipped onto another axis by placing a chain drive perpendictular to the direction of the other shafts"
		""
		"{image:minecraft:item/chain width:25 height:25 align:center}"
		""
		"&oPonder for more details&r"
	]
