	quest.7146D6928EB5420E.quest_desc: [
		"You're actually capable of sqeezing even more out of your generators! "
		"By applying a second source of current to your generator, you're able to boost the output of the generator even further, at the expense of additional heat."
		""
		"This happens because you increase the electromagentic field around our coils, therefore allowing our rotor to transfer more rotational energy into electrical energy."
		""
		"The current must be generated by a secondary source, so you cannot connect more of the generators own current into the generator for more output. (This is because you technically already \"excite\" the generator by connecting the coils to the commutator, the rheostat you used to build a shunt generator just limits that current.)"
	]
	quest.7146D6928EB5420E.quest_subtitle: "Excite a Generator With Additional Current"
	quest.7146D6928EB5420E.title: "Generator Excitation"
	quest.716C303ED6AA210C.quest_desc: [
		"Create: Central Kitchen allows the player to use create components to interact with cooking stations. Valid boiler/heating blocks allow the player to heat these stations too."
		""
		"&oPonder for more details&r"
	]
	quest.716C303ED6AA210C.quest_subtitle: "Obtain Equipment nessacary to automate cooking"
	quest.716C303ED6AA210C.title: "Automated Grilling"
	quest.7194E2C922E21EFB.quest_desc: [
		"Drills are a great all rounder Contraption Mechanism, they will break anything in front of them!"
		"Usable without being attatched to a contraption too, come up with some ideas!"
		"[Hint]: use to make an automated cobblestone farm!"
