	quest.73A5E64076F9866D.quest_desc: [
		"Using what you've learned, it's possible to construct a dual axis, entire chunk quarry miner. Using a double set of gantries, rope pullies, gear shifts and clutches- Build an autonomous miner capable of descending all the way to bedrock, completely terraforming and establishing your claim on this land."
		""
		"(Quarry miners have the advantage over autonomous drills because it is possible to increase mining speed up to 256 rpm)"
	]
	quest.73A5E64076F9866D.quest_subtitle: "Build a chunk miner!"
	quest.73A5E64076F9866D.title: "Bedrock Quarries!?!?!"
	quest.745654045ECE6B96.quest_desc: [
		"Look up \"Dual Wishbone\" or just \"Wishbone\" suspension. Should be easy to make with only pivots and springs."
		""
		"Alternatively, You can grab a suspension key!"
		"This gives you lots of control over how your wheels and tracks work!"
		"I very much reccomend you read the description of the suspension key so you know what to do."
		"To change position, click the wheel/track mount face. vertical faces move the attactched body vertically, horizontal faces move them into and out of the mount."
	]
	quest.745654045ECE6B96.quest_subtitle: "Obtain a spring/build a custom suspension setup"
	quest.745654045ECE6B96.title: "Suspended Suspense..."
	quest.7460A85443533B56.quest_desc: [
		"Same gimmick as the basin heater, electrically expensive heating. This time, it allows for bulk processing through fans!"
		"Capable of cooking foods at low power, and smelting ores at higher power!"
		""
		"&oPonder for more details&r"
