	quest.7824C15F0C4A3934.quest_desc: [
		"Both the Fuse and breaker serve 1 purpose, and that is to \"trip\" an electrical circuit in the case too much current passes through."
		"The Fuse will burn out and takes time to trip, needing to have a portion replaced."
		"The Breaker can be triggered through redstone, and does not have to be replaced"
	]
