	quest.7890068714303386.quest_desc: [
		"Chain conveyers act like chain drives in that rotation follows the same axis of rotation. However, chain drives operate across &nlong distances&r and allow for easier [su] transmission."
		""
		"&oPonder for more details&r"
		""
		""
		"{@pagebreak}"
		""
		"You can also connect chains to flanged chaindrive blocks and cogs! These cannot be ridden and cannot have frogports connect to them, but they allow for some crazy connections!"
	]
