	quest.7A3BA931B8390732.quest_desc: [
		"Ever wanted to make veihicles? Floating buildings? Custom Tools?"
		"The Create:Aeronautics mod allows us to do that! These \"Physics Contraptions\" (named sub-levels by the engine) behave almost like typical create mod contraptions, yet they can move ANYWHERE! These are perfect for creating veihicles to allow for efficent over (and under) world travel."
		""
		"However, you need to have physics to mess around with all of that. Obtain a physics contraption and:"
		""
		"&oPonder for more details&r"
		""
		""
		""
		"{image:simulated:item/spring width:25 height:25 align:center}"
	]
