		"Item filters have 3 types:"
		""
		"-List filters *Allows the player to place a variety of items inside, but the player must supply each item premitted*"
		""
		"-Attribute filters *Allows the player to filter items based off of item tags*"
		""
		"-Package filters *Allows the player to filter item packages based off of address*"
		""
		"&oPonder for more information&r"
	]
